  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BE WARNED: Driving mechanics of this game is NOT recommended for the beginners. It is recommended that players have experience with complex/compound controls in VR and some driving experience. </h2><br><br>Island Explorer is a short VR driving experience where you are on a secluded island with nothing to disturb you:  no quests, no tasks, and no enemies. Just you, your thoughts, and nature… with some relaxing tunes. <br><br><strong>Interactive utility vehicle</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201640/extras/374cc23d99f10b6bcf14baa707bb6d64.poster.avif?t=1684277901\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201640/extras/374cc23d99f10b6bcf14baa707bb6d64.webm?t=1684277901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201640/extras/374cc23d99f10b6bcf14baa707bb6d64.mp4?t=1684277901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>H-Shifter, introducing the first ever VR Manual shifting</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201640/extras/4d599699e84069758352e2e3cd4726a1.poster.avif?t=1684277901\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201640/extras/4d599699e84069758352e2e3cd4726a1.webm?t=1684277901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201640/extras/4d599699e84069758352e2e3cd4726a1.mp4?t=1684277901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Enjoy the scenery</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared